{"tid":1631948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎之前 放低情緒一齊討論下之後點做","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:56.000Z","uid":129529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94c11bd17bead713b34db0ad77136f3c4ad37bd3","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:57.000Z","msg":"我認為今次推呢個蒙面法 係想我地有更激烈既情緒同行為<br />\n從而令到人權法係美國得唔到支持。<br />\n<br />\n所以港共今次除左試行緊急法，另一個目標就係人權法。<br />\n<br />\n佢一早預咗呢幾日必定會有遊行，示威，衝動。<br />\n希望有更多畫面比人睇到，減低人權法通過可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而有鑒於呢幾日，大家都幫各中資副建幫裝修好多鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望多d解釋點解咁做，點解呢d鋪會成為對象，最簡單裝修完 即刻貼文宣係門口 側邊 又可以比記者影 傳媒睇。 <br />\n<br />\n我絕對相信前線，不過都提一句要小心亂黎既人。<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我少少既睇法，希望大家討論下運動去向我再整合一下。<br />\n<br />\n係發夢果到我有幾點想講。<br />\n<br />\n第一，唔好再放行任車，必須要佢調頭。今日大家都見到咩事，唔講了。希望早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔該，我求下你地所有人唔好戴得個死人口罩，特別係落雨果陣。落場第一樣就係要識保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n第三，我冇野講，我冇野post。發完夢，不論幾時都好 行街 搭車 食飯 邊到都好 ，冇人想知你去過邊 做過咩。好好守住呢條規則，記得冇野講。<br />\n<br />\n第四，反跟蹤。唔好覺得換咗衫就好安全，未返到去都要提高警覺。 提早落車行，轉第二條路線反去，留意有冇人跟 等等 用多d唔同既方法保護自己。<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有其他 呢幾項係特別想講"},{"pid":"d1adb8fd63c436f877b1dd1486197189ae3d3191","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cb3d3737dafa1d4179581223ded484d1a00ccbfd","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42a9b6abf4a5bba4eeefdd3be8803adf9bdd665b","tid":1631948,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"a643bca3897803070915e12736edb20f7d2577d7","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eacbb6c54ef313c22ca2950e0f25985a99fc6737","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e84b34419b6f6a9479abfa98247b04a8d861a23","tid":1631948,"uid":294083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非ready就入<br />\n大把野比你地做，有曬分工的"},{"pid":"b39d8a9150879b86b992774ec9e02af9a188931f","tid":1631948,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eade32b438a1abee10735518045c5613c193617","tid":1631948,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"人權法過之前休養生息, <br />\n可以多D宣傳類既活動<br />\n唔好俾港共既激將法成功<br />\n反正過左之後佢地只不過係一個太監<br />\n要打人當然要係佢地最虛弱果陣打<br />\n冇必要硬碰硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2161246f30d916c51b6c1f04ccff8a8a08ab965e","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bc542defd63febf84645c57f8e9c49cbfe7f518","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc18cd4b48f9f6032bdbf39c6cfebb34b76e4d78","tid":1631948,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}